<title>UK: TABLE-Body Shop year pre-excepts profit up.</title>
<headline>TABLE-Body Shop year pre-excepts profit up.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year to March 1</p>
<p>			   (million stg unless stated)</p>
<p> Shr (pence)		9.2		    vs 9.8</p>
<p> Dividend (pence)	 3.2		    vs N/A</p>
<p> Total dividend (pence) 4.7		    vs 3.4</p>
<p> Pretax		     31.7		   vs 32.7</p>
<p> Retail Sales	     622.5		  vs 577.5</p>
<p>NOTE - Above 1996 results included an exceptional provision of 6.5 million stg. Excluding the charge, pre-tax profit was 38.2 million stg versus 32.7 million stg.</p>
<p>Analysts had forecast pre-tax profits in a range between 36.5 and 39.0 million stg.</p>
<p>Full company name - Body Shop International Plc. -London Newsroom +44 171 542 7717</p>
